sparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> ASK  WHERE {         res:Cola rdf:type dbo:Beverage . }

QALD question: Quando è morta la principessa Diana?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?d WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana,_Princess_of_Wales> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/deathDate> ?d . }

QALD question: Dove si produce vino frizzante in Francia?
sparql:
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> 
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri
WHERE {
        ?uri dbo:wineProduced res:Sparkling_wine .
        ?uri dbo:location res:France .
}
